  "title": "Urgent!! Storekeeper - Perm | Up to $2100 | Mon-Fri | West",
  "description": "<p><strong>Urgent!! Storekeeper - Perm | Up to $2100 | Mon-Fri |\nWest</strong></p><p>Salary: Up to $2,100</p><p>Working hours: Mon–Fri Office Hours | 8:00am – 5:00pm</p><p>Location: West | Jurong East </p><p>We are currently hiring a Storekeeper / Warehouse\nAssistant to support production operations through accurate material handling, inventory control, and logistics coordination.</p><p><strong>🧾 Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, check, count, store, and issue raw materials, parts, and finished goods accurately using the ERP system</li><li>Perform inventory cycle counts and stocktakes, ensuring accurate inventory records</li><li>Maintain good housekeeping standards and systematic storage of warehouse items</li><li>Prepare shipping documents and pack finished goods according to standard packing and labelling procedures</li><li>Ensure compliance with workplace safety standards and SOPs</li><li>Carry out other warehouse and logistics duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>✅ Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of storekeeping or warehouse experience</li><li>Forklift licence is an advantage (training can be provided for suitable candidates)</li><li>Comfortable with basic system usage and inventory tracking</li><li>Able to communicate effectively with team members and stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>💰 Salary & Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Monthly Salary: Up to $2,100</li><li>Stable work schedule</li><li>Training provided (including forklift course, if required)</li></ul><p><strong>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</strong></p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to: <a href=\"mailto:Vanessa.chua@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</a></p><p>Please include your <strong>availability, notice period, and expected salary</strong>.</p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by Hrnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
